title: #92Noon! Nordo in for PA!
description: The Christmas Blizzard is on its way, and the Vikings are ill prepared, both literally and metaphorically. Ron Johnson rescheduled his work out to be in studio. The Athletic's, Jon Krawczynski talks Wolves ahead of the opener tonight. And the 'Matt Birk Bit' in studio.
